race.description: Greenfields Lodge At Magic Millions Maiden
race.comment: EIGHTYSEVEN LAD (2) the fitness gave out at Ascot on debut, but he found a place at Pinjarra Scarpside second-up over 1200m and will be better for that. Pike is a key jockey switch and he can position forward. Steps up to 1400m and will get every chance to run it out. LA NOCCIOLA (9) was quickly back on track beaten a whisker this track/trip. She makes it tough for herself by giving way starts but her figures are strong. WAHOOCHINO (3) resumed in the same race beaten a whisker after settling in the back half of the field. He's sharply improved and will be fitter. He can make the finish if the inside gate is managed. PLAYING FREE (1) is third-up and we should see more from him today. Has pieces of form that would see him very competitive.
